<h2 id="zero-shadow-day">Zero Shadow Day</h2>

<p>I co-wrote and illustrated a poster for <i>Zero Shadow Day</i> 2018, to be used in programs for school kids.  I conducted a couple such programs in Chennai.</p>

<p><img src="../images/science/ZSD_poster.jpg" class="shrinkToFit" /></p>

